product.productName: Kodak 4" x 6" Gloss Inkjet Photo Paper, 100-Pack
product.shortDescription: Bring memories to life on Kodak Photo Paper, and easily share them with friends and relatives, proudly display them in your home and office or add them to your scrapbook or other craft project. They're specifically designed to work with almost any inkjet printer to yield high-quality and professional-looking photos. This printer photo paper comes in a conveniently-sized 100-pack, providing a steady supply of quality paper for vacation snapshots, special event photographs, everyday milestones and more. This special paper features a smooth, glossy finish that gives the photos a very polished and professional look. It also quickly absorbs ink, so the pictures dry almost instantly with no smudging or smearing. Each sheet of 4" x 6" gloss inkjet photo paper comes from the original manufacturer, so you can buy it with confidence. Fine photograph and inkjet printers are all available separately, and these inkjet cartridges are easy to install in only minutes.

product.productName: Inland Pro Photo Glossy Paper 5" x 7" 50 Pack
product.shortDescription: Get professional quality printing at home or at the office with the Inland Pro Photo Glossy Paper. This crisp paper stock is ideally suited for printing color photos and images. The Inland paper, 5" x 7", has a heavier 195g weight with superior brightness, opacity and optical density. Each sheet has a remarkable 5760 dpi, making digital photos come to life with each printing job. The photo printing paper, 50 pack has a high gloss finish. The paper is also 80 percent water-resistant for added longevity.
